================================================================================
  EXPERIMENT 1: Matrix Size Sweep (TP_DEGREE=4)
================================================================================

  --- Size 2048x2048 ---
  [DP] 1 core: host=0.136 ms, dev=0.147 ms
  [TP=4] 4 cores: host=0.313 ms, dev=0.193 ms

  --- Size 4096x4096 ---
  [DP] 1 core: host=0.940 ms, dev=0.975 ms
  [TP=4] 4 cores: host=0.410 ms, dev=0.467 ms

  --- Size 8192x8192 ---
  [DP] 1 core: host=7.964 ms, dev=8.018 ms
  [TP=4] 4 cores: host=2.209 ms, dev=2.425 ms

  --- Size 16384x16384 ---
  [DP] 1 core: host=86.851 ms, dev=86.920 ms
  [TP=4] 4 cores: host=17.292 ms, dev=17.499 ms

  ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  Experiment 1 Results (TP_DEGREE=4):
  ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
     Size DP 1-core (ms) TP 4-core (ms)  Speedup Efficiency
  ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
     2048          0.136          0.313     0.44x      10.9%
